data.description: Fully updated and move-in ready property in South Springfield!  Lots of new!  New roof, new windows, new water heater, new flooring and updates and upgrades galore!  All work completed by a professional contractor.   All kitchen appliances included.  Mature landscaping in the back yard that includes a lovely shed!  You are not going to want to miss out on this one!
